graph TB
    subgraph "Llama Stack Operator"
        Controller[Controller Manager<br/>Deployment]
        LlamaDistController[LlamaStackDistribution<br/>Controller]
        MetricsService[Metrics Service<br/>:8443/TCP HTTPS]
        HealthProbes[Health Probes<br/>:8081/TCP HTTP]
        KustomizeEngine[Kustomize Engine<br/>In-Process]
        ConfigWatcher[ConfigMap Watcher<br/>Controller Watch]
        NetPolMgr[NetworkPolicy Manager<br/>Reconciler]

        Controller -->|reconciles| LlamaDistController
        Controller -->|exposes| MetricsService
        Controller -->|provides| HealthProbes
        LlamaDistController -->|uses| KustomizeEngine
        Controller -->|watches| ConfigWatcher
        LlamaDistController -->|manages| NetPolMgr
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        LlamaStackCR[LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>llamastack.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "Managed Resources"
        Deployment[Llama Stack Deployment]
        Service[Llama Stack Service<br/>:8321/TCP]
        PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>10Gi default]
        HPA[HorizontalPodAutoscaler<br/>optional]
        PDB[PodDisruptionBudget<br/>optional]
        Ingress[Ingress<br/>optional]
        NetPol[NetworkPolicy<br/>feature flag]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>:6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>ServiceMonitor]
        Ollama[Ollama Server<br/>:11434/TCP HTTP]
        vLLM[vLLM Server<br/>:8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS]
        HuggingFace[HuggingFace Hub<br/>:443/TCP HTTPS]
        Registry[Container Registry<br/>:443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH/RHOAI"
        CABundle[odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>ConfigMap]
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Istio - Optional]
    end

    User[User/CI] -->|creates| LlamaStackCR
    LlamaStackCR -->|watched by| LlamaDistController

    LlamaDistController -->|creates/manages| Deployment
    LlamaDistController -->|creates/manages| Service
    LlamaDistController -->|creates/manages| PVC
    LlamaDistController -->|creates/manages| HPA
    LlamaDistController -->|creates/manages| PDB
    LlamaDistController -->|creates/manages| Ingress
    NetPolMgr -->|creates/deletes| NetPol

    Controller -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI
    MetricsService -->|scraped by| Prometheus

    Deployment -->|inference requests| Ollama
    Deployment -->|inference requests| vLLM
    vLLM -->|downloads models| HuggingFace
    Deployment -->|pulls images| Registry
    Deployment -->|uses TLS certs| CABundle
    Deployment -.->|optional| ServiceMesh

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LlamaDistController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LlamaStackCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Deployment fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Service fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Ollama fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style vLLM fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CABundle fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
